"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Haiti's government declared a state of emergency and curfew after 4,000 inmates escaped from prisons. Armed gangs control 80% of Port-au-Prince and demand the prime minister's resignation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Haiti Prison Break and Gang Violence\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno de Hait\u00ed declar\u00f3 un estado de emergencia y toque de queda despu\u00e9s de que 4,000 presos escaparon de las c\u00e1rceles. Pandillas armadas controlan el 80% de Puerto Pr\u00edncipe y exigen la renuncia del primer ministro.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Haiti Prison Break and Gang Violence\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kamala Harris, America's vice-president, called for an immediate ceasefire in Gaza and urged Israel to increase aid supplies. She is set to meet with Israel's war cabinet member Benny Gantz.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ceasefire Efforts in Gaza\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kamala Harris, la vicepresidenta de Estados Unidos, pidi\u00f3 un alto el fuego inmediato en Gaza y inst\u00f3 a Israel a aumentar el suministro de ayuda. Est\u00e1 programada para reunirse con el miembro del gabinete de guerra de Israel, Benny Gantz.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ceasefire Efforts in Gaza\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Commission fined Apple \u20ac1.8bn for breaching competition law by limiting information on other firms' music streaming services. Apple plans to appeal the ruling.\",            \"english_title\": \"EU Fine on Apple for Competition Law Breach\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Comisi\u00f3n Europea mult\u00f3 a Apple con 1.8 mil millones de euros por infringir la ley de competencia al limitar la informaci\u00f3n sobre los servicios de transmisi\u00f3n de m\u00fasica de otras empresas. Apple planea apelar la decisi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EU Fine on Apple for Competition Law Breach\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Shares in TSMC rose by 5.2% to a record high, boosting its market capitalisation to $597bn. The surge is driven by developments in generative artificial intelligence.\",            \"english_title\": \"TSMC Stock Price Surge\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las acciones de TSMC subieron un 5.2% a un m\u00e1ximo hist\u00f3rico, aumentando su capitalizaci\u00f3n de mercado a $597 mil millones. El aumento est\u00e1 impulsado por avances en inteligencia artificial generativa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"TSMC Stock Price Surge\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Germany's defence minister accused Vladimir Putin of a hybrid disinformation attack after Russia released a recording of a private meeting on military aid to Ukraine. China aims to stabilize pork prices to combat deflation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Germany-Russia Dispute and China's Pork Price Stabilization\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ministro de defensa de Alemania acus\u00f3 a Vladimir Putin de un ataque h\u00edbrido de desinformaci\u00f3n despu\u00e9s de que Rusia publicara una grabaci\u00f3n de una reuni\u00f3n privada sobre ayuda militar a Ucrania. China tiene como objetivo estabilizar los precios del cerdo para combatir la deflaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Germany-Russia Dispute and China's Pork Price Stabilization\"        }    ]}"